text: Aoke-Langalanga is a constituency of the Solomon Islands. It is in the Malaita Province. It was created in 1993. ==Election results== 2019 general election Candidate Party Votes Matthew Wale Democratic Party 3,712 Vincent Anisi Kadere Party 2,770 Feradatolo David Independent 1,431 Invalid/blank votes 10 Total 7,923 Registered voters 8,841 Source: SIEC ==References== Category:Solomon Islands parliamentary constituencies
